page.title: 02DAY IN MY LIFE CONTINUED
page.content: My favourite dinner is sausage beans and chips and for pudding I like butterscotch tart best.In afternoon school we watch junior maths.Then we play rounders.After play we have a story read to us. At present it is Stig of the Dump by Clive King. At 3.15p.m. we put up our chair an sing good afternoon. After school I play . I ride my B.M.X. bike and also play in my paddling pool. I have hamburder and chips or a salad for tea. Then i do my recorder practice and after this watch television. My favourite programmes are Dog Tanyon, Doctor Who , and the Kenny Everett show. I read a book in bed and go to sleep at 8.30p.m.
